review_blob: Heres what you do, just pour in trashcan.  I still have a headache from it.
Loved this beer.  Never thought I would like a pilsner but now want to try some from smaller brewers.

Sometimes, you just got to have the beer that is nostalgic.  This was the first beer that my dad gave me.  Granted, Bud Light is mass produced and cheap to buy, but it still has that iconic beer taste that brings me back to my first beer.
Very nice aroma and little spicey for my taste, but still a very good beer.
